    <h2>What the Archive<br>Is and Does</h2>
    <p>The objects in this exhibition come from the physical collection of the Textiles + Fiber area at the University of Kansas. They were acquired over decades, by hands other than mine, for reasons not always recorded. This section is an attempt to be honest about that history.</p>

