    <h3>On the Violence of the Archive</h3>
    <p>Archives preserve and archives distort. An object pulled from its context of use, renamed by discipline, and held in a university collection carries that history whether or not the record acknowledges it. This project doesn't resolve that problem. It tries to stay inside it — to make visible the translation chains that brought each object here, and to be honest about what has been lost along the way.</p>

